column1: Certain provisions of our Certificate of Incorporation and ylaws and of the DGCL could have the effect of delaying deferring
discouraging another party from acquiring control of us. In particular our capital structure concentrates ownership of our voting
stock in the hands of Larry Sergey and Eric. These provisions which are summarized below are expected to discourage coerciv
